
run "qmake" first after each checkout
   $ qmake

If you want Debug-Code, run qmake with the DEBUG=1 Parameter
   $ qmake DEBUG=1

Compile with make
   $ make

Run PiTres
   $ build/PiTres

The Database is stored relatively from your RunPath unter ./data/userlist.sqlite
This will be configurable in a later release...

For LDAP-Attributes see http://wiki.piratecomic.net/wiki/Mitglieder_DB/LDAP_Database_Fields
